{
  "stem": "719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came from Auschwitz, into Bedzin, into Sosnowiec-- and so all these Jewish little towns around us to settle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And little did we know-- nobody said anything, nobody understood why they are transporting all these people out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They started to build the destroying-- the camp to destroy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The program was how to-- the final solution-- what to do with all these Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So eventually, they started to send them out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I didn't hear about Auschwitz until I left home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And even then, when I was in camp, there were some women coming in from Auschwitz to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were scared to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They said, there are kindergartens, that Auschwitz has-- has homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were afraid to tell us the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had head shaved for hygiene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They wear uniform, because we had no way of changing clothes and stuff.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was the excuse.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But never did they talk about what's really-- all crematoriums and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We did find out later on in the camps, but it wasn't-- later on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in 1942-- [SIGHS] there were rumors about a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto was supposed to be on a field on a-- outside that street where I lived, outside those buildings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those buildings were later on occupied by the non-Jewish resident-- by the Poles-- whoever took over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I wasn't dumb anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what happened is around May-- it was after Passover, 1942-- they-- there was a law to gather all the Jews into one point, and to-- they call it in German a [GERMAN], like a gathering.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It used to be an orphanage-- a Jewish orphanage-- but the kids were gone by then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was very close to a train station.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
